description:
Changes order status to "CONFIRMED" - from "INITIATED, "PENDING", "OFFLINE_PENDING" to "PAID".
Previously confirmed orders (with status "PAID" or "FREE") are not changed.
Confirming previously "INITIATED" or "PENDING" orders triggers an email with the tickets to the buyer (and to additional guests, if relevant and provided).

params.name: fieldset
params.doc: Controls which data is returned. See [Fieldset](https://dev.wix.com/api/rest/wix-events/wix-events/fieldset#wix-events_wix-events_fieldset_order-fieldset).

description: Retrieves and order, including ticket data.
Retrieves a summary of total ticket sales.
Retrieves a list of orders, including ticket data, with basic filter support.

params.name: fields
params.doc: Set of field paths to update.

members.name: inputValues
members.doc: Input values entered upon ticket order.

members.name: fieldset
members.doc: Controls which data is returned. See [Fieldset](https://dev.wix.com/api/rest/wix-events/wix-events/fieldset#wix-events_wix-events_fieldset_order-fieldset).

members.name: contactId
members.doc: Contact ID associated with this guest.

members.name: guestAssigned
members.doc: Whether ticket belongs to assigned guest.

members.name: number
members.doc: Int or floating point number value.

members.name: grandTotal
members.doc:
Total amount of cart after discount, tax, and fees.
Grand total is calculated in the following order:
1. Total prices of all items in the cart are calculated.
2. Discount is subtracted from the cart (if applicable).
3. Tax is added (if applicable).
4. Wix service fee is added.

members.name: previewUrl
members.doc: URL to invoice preview. Returned only if order is paid.

members.name: revenue
members.doc: Total revenue, excluding fees. (Taxes and payment provider fees are not deducted).

members.name: subTotal
members.doc: Total cart amount before discount, tax, and fees.

members.name: discount
members.doc: Discount applied to the line item.

members.name: total
members.doc: Total price for line items. Always equal to price * quantity.

members.name: fieldset
members.doc: Controls which data is returned. See [Fieldset](https://dev.wix.com/api/rest/wix-events/wix-events/fieldset#wix-events_wix-events_fieldset_order-fieldset).

members.name: searchPhrase
members.doc: Textual search filter - search is performed on "full_name", "email" and "order_number".

members.name: total
members.doc: Total orders matching the given filters.

members.name: currency
members.doc: ISO 4217 format of the currency i.e. `USD`.

members.name: value
members.doc: Monetary amount. Decimal string with a period as a decimal separator (e.g., 3.99). Optionally, a single (-), to indicate that the amount is negative.

members.name: anonymized
members.doc: Whether the order is anonymized by GDPR delete.

members.name: checkoutForm
members.doc: Checkout form response. When each purchased ticket is assigned to a guest, guest forms are returned for each ticket, and buyer info is returned.

members.name: confirmed
members.doc: Whether the order is confirmed (triggered once payment gateway processes the payment and funds reach the merchant's account).

members.name: contactId
members.doc: Contact ID of buyer (resolved using email address).

members.name: fullyCheckedIn
members.doc: Whether all tickets in order are checked-in.

members.name: method
members.doc: Payment method used for purchase, e.g., "payPal", "creditCard", etc.

members.name: snapshotId
members.doc:
Payment snapshot ID.
Empty for FREE order.

members.name: anonymized
members.doc: Whether order was anonymized by GDPR delete.

members.name: memberId
members.doc: Member ID associated with this order.

members.name: timestamp
members.doc: Order deleted timestamp in ISO UTC format.

members.name: triggeredByAnonymizeRequest
members.doc: Whether event was triggered by GDPR delete request.

members.name: archived

members.name: checkInUrl
members.doc:
Ticket check-in URL.
Shown as QR code image in PDF.
Format: `https://www.wixevents.com/check-in/{ticket number},{event id}`
Example: `https://www.wixevents.com/check-in/AAAA-AAAA-BB021,00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000`

members.name: orderArchived

members.name: walletPassUrl
